divs: Sighting DetailsPhotograph taken on Xmas Day, from Coyle Park, Point Chevalier, Auckland, New Zealand. Apparent position of object: -36.851982,174.703774 Position of photographer: -36.851982,174.703774 facing West Object was not seen, only noticed once the photograph was viewed later. Sea birds were in the vicinity, and had appeared in shots taken from another vantage point facing East, however none were noticed in other shots taken within seconds of this photograph.
